---
description: CodeDecay repository rules for AI-assisted development
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` before making changes.

Use `.agents/commands/ci-check.md` before opening a PR.

Use `.agents/skills/pr-red-team/SKILL.md` for PR safety reviews and
`.agents/skills/test-quality-review/SKILL.md` when tests are touched.

Preserve CodeDecay constraints:

- no telemetry,
- no required API keys,
- no required LLM/model calls,
- no hidden cloud dependency,
- deterministic baseline behavior.
